### Placements

Dropdown supports different placement options to control where the menu appears relative to the trigger: `topLeft`, `topRight`, `bottomLeft`, `bottomRight`, `top`, `bottom`, `left`, `right`.

<ComponentSource src="dropdown/demo/placements.tsx" __comp__={PlacementsDemo} />

### Trigger

Dropdown supports multiple trigger modes: `click` (default), `hover`, and `contextMenu` (right-click). You can use a single trigger or combine multiple triggers in an array.

<ComponentSource src="dropdown/demo/trigger.tsx" __comp__={TriggerDemo} />

